## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date information, as the situation regarding COVID-19 and public health guidelines is continually evolving. Additionally, the variability in safety measures across different casinos means that findings may not be universally applicable. The reliance on online sources also means that some information may be anecdotal or lack rigorous scientific validation.